  "texts": [
    "Based on them, we filter invalid data that conflict with our curation principles, annotate the safety labels, and write risk descriptions.",
    "Notably, agents in AgentMonitor do not follow ReAct (with only 'action'), so we leave the field of 'thought' as null.",
    "Manual Construction.",
    "We also construct highquality data from human experts.",
    "For one part, to supplement inadequate 'safe' examples, we transform some of the 'unsafe' examples in ToolEmu into 'safe' ones by replacing the risky agent actions with safe ones."
